rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主原來文盲<br />\n只識坐井觀天<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293439456a8170ba3724a5229ea67e2de5b10e4a","tid":927924,"uid":225011,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"没错，简体字因笔划所限，确实没有像繁体字般「爱」中有「心」那样的效果。但是，把这作为衡量一种字体的价值的唯一标准，难道不是太狭窄了吗？我认为我们也是得考虑一下其他因素的。比方说，简体字的笔划比繁体字少，便能让最多的文盲在最短的时间内掌握读写能力，对我国成立后的农村扫盲行动 ，是起了关键的作用了。"},{"pid":"10cd983dcda491e52b79fc78a385396976301a16","tid":927924,"uid":142026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"293439456a8170ba3724a5229ea67e2de5b10e4a","tid":927924,"uid":225011,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"没错，简体字因笔划所限，确实没有像繁体字般「爱」中有「心」那样的效果。但是，把这作为衡量一种字体的价值的唯一标准，难道不是太狭窄了吗？我认为我们也是得考虑一下其他因素的。比方说，简体字的笔划比繁体字少，便能让最多的文盲在最短的时间内掌握读写能力，对我国成立后的农村扫盲行动 ，是起了关键的作用了。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"想快不如以後轉埋用漢語拼音, 直頭棄用漢字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d056f876cbc6db7affb771fe9dbf245c34f0aa2","tid":927924,"uid":101433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"293439456a8170ba3724a5229ea67e2de5b10e4a","tid":927924,"uid":225011,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"没错，简体字因笔划所限，确实没有像繁体字般「爱」中有「心」那样的效果。但是，把这作为衡量一种字体的价值的唯一标准，难道不是太狭窄了吗？我认为我们也是得考虑一下其他因素的。比方说，简体字的笔划比繁体字少，便能让最多的文盲在最短的时间内掌握读写能力，对我国成立后的农村扫盲行动 ，是起了关键的作用了。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"點解要快學習 而唔係全面學習<br />\n咩都化簡晒無左當中字既意義<br />\n學習文字間接學習到文化 <br />\n文盲如果真係有心學 唔化簡都學到"},{"pid":"37b59fcae0e0a59646617e0ac2cbbb4a50ada425","tid":927924,"uid":223593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"真係慘, 咁既垃圾已經算係中國最偉大既發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a3a7a15f06c9b0385fa022939081168eb29d92","tid":927924,"uid":225011,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"拼音也不是不能用，可以这样一来，我们便会失去了方块字阅读速度快的好处了。而且中文字那么多，一个拼音多个意思的问题要怎样解决？简体字必然是最好的折衷！"},{"pid":"95e4520e82d125b16573b55a465b558f769c6e93","tid":927924,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://geekiam.files.wordpress.com/2007/02/fuckgood.jpg?w=510\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeekiam.files.wordpress.com%2F2007%2F02%2Ffuckgood.jpg%3Fw%3D510&h=0d1b23c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b891164c24d1879d37229a715302afc17fa51500","tid":927924,"uid":141148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"將自己身分證改撚左做簡體先啦<br />\n屌你老母 講經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bc179d7a624feb7ce8d02eb2e816cfb7e8cfc8","tid":927924,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"734869558a128f5a71ccf620f2fa972ab80c2f6f","tid":927924,"uid":3326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"943ad4707c64129fde4b2a355241ef41a8a35776","tid":927924,"uid":225011,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"477952af359bf0682ddf15951f7499db347ac009","tid":927924,"uid":161190,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"操你媽B"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"没文化，只懂得骂脏话吗？反对的就拿出你的论点和论据。"}